column2: SELECT search_id AS up_id, ra AS up_ra, dec AS up_dec FROM MyDB.tmp1  CREATE TABLE #tmp ( 	up_id int, 	objid bigint ) INSERT INTO #tmp EXEC spGetNeighbors # -- # -- default. min=#   INSERT INTO MyDB.tmp1# SELECT DISTINCT tmp.*  FROM #tmp tmp 	INNER JOIN      DR1#.PhotoPrimary po ON po.objid      = tmp.objid 	LEFT OUTER JOIN DR1#.Photoz       pz ON pz.objid      = po.objid 	LEFT OUTER JOIN DR1#.SpecObj      sp ON sp.bestobjid  = po.objid 	LEFT OUTER JOIN DR1#.WISE_xmatch  wx ON wx.sdss_objid = po.objid 	LEFT OUTER JOIN DR1#.WISE_allsky  wa ON wa.cntr       = wx.wise_cntr 	LEFT OUTER JOIN DR1#.TwoMassXSC   tm ON tm.objid      = po.objid 	LEFT OUTER JOIN DR1#.FIRST        ft ON ft.objid      = po.objid WHERE  -- do not only use po.clean = # since sometimes it contains unknown check. 	( po.clean = #  	OR ( 		((po.flags & #) != #)        -- detected in BINNED1 		AND ((po.flags & #) = #) -- not NOPROFILE, PEAKCENTER, 		                                      -- NOTCHECKED, PSF_FLUX_INTERP, 		                                      -- SATURATED, or BAD_COUNTS_ERROR 		                                      -- if you want to accept objects with 		                                      -- interpolation problems for PSF mags, 		                                      -- change this to: 		                                      -- AND ((flags & #) = #) 		AND (((po.flags & #) = #) OR (po.psfmagerr_g <= #)) 		        -- not DEBLEND_NOPEAK or small PSF error 		        -- (substitute psfmagerr in other band as appropriate) 		AND (((po.flags & #) = #) OR (po.flags & #) = #) 		        -- not INTERP_CENTER or not COSMIC_RAY. omit this AND clause if you 		        -- want to accept objects with interpolation problems for PSF mags. 		) 	) 	AND (po.calibStatus_g & #) != # 	AND (po.calibStatus_r & #) != # 	AND (po.calibStatus_i & #) != # 	AND po.cmodelmagerr_g <= # -- SNR>=# 	AND po.cmodelmagerr_r <= # -- SNR>=# 	AND po.cmodelmagerr_i <= # -- SNR>=# 	AND po.extinction_i <= #  	AND wx.wise_cntr IS NULL 	-- AND ( wa.w1cc_map = # AND wa.w2cc_map = # AND wa.w3cc_map = # AND wa.w4cc_map = # ) 	-- AND ( wa.w1m     >= # AND wa.w2m     >= # AND wa.w3m     >= # AND wa.w4m     >= # ) 	-- AND ( wa.w3m   >= # ) 	-- AND ( wa.w1snr   >= # AND wa.w2snr   >= # AND wa.w3snr   >= # AND wa.w4snr   >= # ) 	-- AND ( wa.w3snr >= # ) 	-- AND ( wx.match_dist <= # )  -- ( wa.w1snr >= # AND wa.w2snr >= # AND wa.w3snr >= # AND wa.w4snr >= # ) --  AND ( po.type = dbo.fPhotoType(&&&) OR po.type = dbo.fPhotoType(&&&) ) --  AND ( sp.class = &&& OR sp.class = &&& OR sp.class IS NULL ) ORDER BY tmp.up_id, tmp.objid
